  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All female patients 18 years of age or older undergoing surgery for any gynecologic
             procedure which the peritoneum is entered and general anesthesia is administered.

          -  Disease State will not affect inclusion in the study. Women with previous surgeries or
             other medical conditions will be included as will those undergoing an initial
             operation.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient deemed legally incompetent to sign their own consent

          -  Women under the age of 18

          -  Patients lacking their own or a false set of teeth
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
